snippet.title: Pajama Sam 2: Thunder and Lightning Aren't so Frightening - Official Trailer | PS4 Games
snippet.description:
Pajama Sam 2: Thunder and Lightning Aren't so Frightening is coming to PS4 on November 3rd!

Join Pajama Sam, the world's youngest superhero as he journeys to World Wide Weather, the storm-stirring factory in the sky!

#ps4games #ps4
